Class Teacher

java.lang.Object
classes.User
classes.Employee
classes.Teacher
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<User>
public class Teacher extends Employee
Intranet System's Teacher model. Represents the instructor of the certain course or courses. Has User and Employee fields, leading with self specific fields such as title and experience in teaching. Courses have students and teacher must evaluate their skills.
